<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1564690-i-m-only-about-50-pages-in-and-so-far-it-s">I&#39;m only about 50 pages in and so far it&#39;s not really doing a whole lot for me but I see such incredible reviews. Does the book get better as it goes or am I just missing the point if it doesn&#39;t grip me straight from the get-go?</a>
</div>
