<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    SPOILER ALERT!!!! (Scroll down to view)<br />.<br />.<br />.<br />.<br />.<br />.<br />Thank you for reading, and I'm so glad that you loved it. My answer isn't being flagged with a spoiler al<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    SPOILER ALERT!!!! (Scroll down to view)<br />.<br />.<br />.<br />.<br />.<br />.<br />Thank you for reading, and I'm so glad that you loved it. My answer isn't being flagged with a spoiler alert, so I'm doing that manually here. Scroll down for the answer.<br />.<br />.<br />.<br />Pak and Yoo did not get divorced, at least not yet! I think Young is considering his prison sentence as a good separation of sorts, a time when they can both re-evaluate their relationship and their lives in general. I hope that's helpful!<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
